"A clarion call has been made by the students and none of us must claim to have a solution."We must never give the students the impression that they are crazy or ignorant.""We must explain to them that there is a plan clear plan."Mogoeng was speaking at the O.R Tambo lecture in Johannesburg on Thursday."We all have to be constructively engaged on finding a solution " Mogoeng said."We don't want those institutions to be burnt down."